{"tid":1530693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽完個局長記招有感而發","createTime":"2019-09-02T04:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T04:54:10.000Z","uid":152159,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce4b5d0fedf38b6bcd98544783c3cc32d86b363a","tid":1530693,"uid":152159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"班官比黑警更可惡<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7195b85009549f7e70cb5f24cecbf775662238","tid":1530693,"uid":76538,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:39:25.000Z","msg":"冇學生用成個暑假去幫我地抗爭, 我地點撚樣捱到今日??<br />\n<br />\n就係今日, 佢地著番校服, 被迫服從呢個洗腦既教育制度<br />\n學校用佢地權力去迫害我地既學生<br />\n記大過?? 狗圍學校???<br />\n<br />\n佢地幫我地付出左咁多, 依加佢地需要幫手呀!!!<br />\n我地要話俾佢地知, 係學校唔洗驚, 出面既哥哥姐姐會幫番你<br />\n<br />\n求下大家, 記底所有懲罰抗爭學生既學校<br />\n今個星期六日, 逐間拆!!!<br />\n入面唔需要有人, 我地係要對呢個制度抗議<br />\n就好似我地拆黨鐵一樣, 幫佢地強制罷課<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">學校敢制裁學生, 我地制裁學校!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n敵人想用恐懼去支配我地抗爭最大既本錢!! 學生呀!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530626</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"78957e3660b03ff412571bfe8abf886469d49fe5","tid":1530693,"uid":152159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d89aa5979dff53b14ccacf63293358c452603ecf","tid":1530693,"uid":152159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:40:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc57dae14539f612bbf7cbafe7c4a5b4335057e4","tid":1530693,"uid":152159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ce188bb3ba789a951ac558aeb86430561e77345","tid":1530693,"uid":152159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"推到有人"},{"pid":"eefd3796e20e72d1434421347809e72cd7b4b8d2","tid":1530693,"uid":152159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB